    • addBox

      void addBox(double minX, double minY, double minZ, double maxX, double maxY, double maxZ)
      add a collision box, expects 0.0 - 16.0 block coords. No complaints about the size, I like using pixels :P
      Parameters:
      minX - minimal x collision
      minY - minimal y collision
      minZ - minimal z collision
      maxX - maximal x collision
      maxY - maximal y collision
      maxZ - maximal z collision
